    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers dependable transportation for those on a budget. The exterior shows some wear, including several scuffs on the bumpers, a few small door dings, and noticeable clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and typical wear on the driver's seat. While it runs and drives well, it is being sold as-is to reflect its age and current cosmetic state.",
